dataUpdate

public ResponseDataUpdate dataUpdate(ParamsDataUpdate params)
Updates existing Data Object if data with specified data_id or data_key already exists. You can specify how to react if specified Data Object already exists with update_method parameter. Possible options: replace - default value. Will delete all Data Object fields and create a new one in its place (no previous data will remain). merge - will not delete/empty previously set data but merge it instead with new data.

Parameters:
params - parameters for request
Returns:
response for this request
